OL,5, A company that made a rifle used in one
OL,6, of the US's deadliest school shootings 
OL,7, has settled with the families of       
OL,8, victims for $73m (#53.9m).             
OL,10,FThe settlement from Remington Arms     
OL,11,Fcomes in response to a lawsuit brought 
OL,12,Fby the families of nine of 26 victims  
OL,13,Fof the 2012 Sandy Hook massacre.       
OL,15,FThe case marks the first time a        
OL,16,Fgun-maker has faced liability for a    
OL,17,Fmass shooting.                         
OL,19,FUntil now, the industry has been       
OL,20,Fenjoyed immunity from litigation.      
